*.tlh
*.tmp
*.vspscc
.builds
*.dotCover
*.vsconfig

# Others
[Bb]in
[Oo]bj
sql
TestResults
*.Cache
ClientBin
stylecop.*
~$*
*.dbmdl
Generated_Code #added for RIA/Silverlight projects

